{"tid":1872212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"招人做抗爭紀錄","createTime":"2020-02-10T03:19:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-12T06:53:36.000Z","uid":268604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f51148669708c14cfd3c14358bab9041eaf48814","tid":1872212,"uid":268604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:19:27.000Z","msg":"我而家進行針對香港「反修例運動」既口述見證計劃，希望紀錄本地唔同持份者既觀點同感受。只要持有香港永久性居民身份證，任何人士都可以參加本計劃。<br />\n<br />\n過程中只會進行錄音同文字紀錄。你可以要求使用化名，及/或進行聲音加工。訪談前，你會填寫一張問卷，同提交一個最令你印象深刻既物件（必須係同反修例運動有關既）。可包括但不限於照片、圖畫、影片、歌曲、詩詞，或實物，訪談問題將會根據嗰個物件設計。<br />\n<br />\n訪談成品將會上傳至 Internet Archive (<a href=\"http://archive.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Farchive.org&d=nNI0xXmu%2FnmsXsjxjv7MVdOI4bCcJ6pqCJTTaBDemLU%3D&h=fe826e41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://archive.org</a>)，一個永久公開的海外網上檔案館，同會以展覽、書籍方式比外國人睇。<br />\n<br />\n有興趣者，請tg 我 @godwontsavetheworld"},{"pid":"2b967f6ad9a26a657c4ec135b7740900132f7780","tid":1872212,"uid":156326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:25:01.000Z","msg":"證明埋自己身份會唔會好啲"},{"pid":"08e8cdb64b8f4597db9d93ae309ebab8f557d427","tid":1872212,"uid":268604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:30:28.000Z","msg":"我係一個係紐約讀緊藝術碩士既準畢業生，今年五月會係學校做一個畢業展，同今次抗爭有關既。"},{"pid":"0ff3a7bfae4f2cff75fb57c91a147d4caafe2d62","tid":1872212,"uid":268604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08e8cdb64b8f4597db9d93ae309ebab8f557d427","tid":1872212,"uid":268604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:30:28.000Z","msg":"我係一個係紐約讀緊藝術碩士既準畢業生，今年五月會係學校做一個畢業展，同今次抗爭有關既。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:33:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1cTgY0R.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1cTgY0R.png&h=9762d4b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95064a15c0ed35b6912101a37305283a0cd01a21","tid":1872212,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-10T03:36:54.000Z